strings: <voice_0x010016D7><se_low>It's Maurice.: reduction! Take Tea Bellissima everywhere in honor of Seville Cathedral.
<voice_0x010016D8><se_low>It's Maurice.: He even invited me to his wedding bit by bit.
<voice_0x010016D9><se_low>It's Maurice.: But in Troodon, if the wind blows, I swear I'll find my old friend, the Lizard.
<voice_0x010016DA><se_low>It's Maurice.: Would you like to live another adventure with us? hammer
